fm: string toGoatLatin(string S) {         string ret;         int m = 1, n = S.size();         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             int j = i + 1;             while (j != n && S[j] != ' ')                 ++j;             string temp;             char t = tolower(S[i]);             bool vowel = (t == 'a' || t == 'e' || t == 'i' || t == 'o' || t == 'u');             if (vowel)                 temp += S[i];             temp += S.substr(i + 1, j - i - 1);             if (!vowel)                 temp += S[i];             temp += "ma";             for (int k = 0; k < m; ++k)                 temp += 'a';             ++m;             i = j;             if(i != n)                 temp += ' ';             ret += temp;         }         return ret;     }

fm: int numFriendRequests(vector<int> &ages) {         int total = 0;         vector<int> age_groups(121, 0), age_sum(121, 0);         for (auto age:ages)             ++age_groups[age];         for (int i = 1; i <= 120; ++i)             age_sum[i] = age_sum[i - 1] + age_groups[i];         for (int i = 1; i <= 120; ++i) {             if (age_groups[i] != 0) {                 int count = age_sum[i] - age_sum[i / 2 + 7];                 if (count > 0)                     total += age_groups[i] * (count - 1);             }         }         return total;     }
